  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of the project is to study the risk of coccidioidomycosis (valley fever) in patients
      receiving anti-TNF and other biologic agents for inflammatory arthritis in Tucson, Arizona.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Retrospective chart review of all patients with an inflammatory arthritis seen at the
      University Rheumatology clinic since January 2000.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
